headline: PPL : Electric Utilities brings its Live Line Electrical Safety Demonstration to the 109th Pennsylvania Farm Show
summary: ALLENTOWN, Pa. - Building on the 109th Pennsylvania Farm Show's theme of Powering Pennsylvania, PPL Electric Utilities engaged attendees in a demonstration of potentially life-saving information...
